WEBVTT

1
00:22:03.670 --> 00:22:05.540 
她的DNA不只是重新排列了
Her DNA didn't just rearrange --

2
00:22:05.540 --> 00:22:07.630 
还加入了额外的大分子链
It contains extra macromolecules.

3
00:22:07.630 --> 00:22:09.340 
我都不知道还有这种可能性
I wouldn't think that even possible.

4
00:22:09.640 --> 00:22:11.760 
-太神奇了  -太可怕了
- That's amazing. - It's horrific.

5
00:22:11.870 --> 00:22:14.180 
我们得确保你没受到任何污染
We need to make sure that you're not contaminated

6
00:22:14.180 --> 00:22:15.740 
或者感染
or infected in any way.

7
00:22:16.300 --> 00:22:17.680 
最坏的情况是什么
What's the worst that could happen?

8
00:22:18.340 --> 00:22:19.480 
一场瘟疫
An epidemic.

9
00:22:20.100 --> 00:22:21.740 
这结论太吓人了吧
That's a pretty harsh conclusion.

10
00:22:21.800 --> 00:22:23.710 
我觉得我有责任
Well, and I feel responsible.

11
00:22:24.260 --> 00:22:25.220 
我们都有
We all do.

12
00:22:25.290 --> 00:22:26.620 
你当时不可能做什么
There's nothing you could have done.

13
00:22:26.620 --> 00:22:27.900 
我本来可以的
Yes, there was.

14
00:22:29.180 --> 00:22:33.230 
我对超能力和外星生物学太好奇了
I was so curious about powers, about unearthly biology,

15
00:22:33.230 --> 00:22:34.450 
我好奇它会引我们到何处
wondering where it might lead,

